quests.desc: Who's got a virtual machine and is about to play through an exciting round of TextWorld? You do! Here is your task for today. First of all, you could, like, go to the east. After that, move south. And then, attempt to go to the east. With that accomplished, go north. With that over with, go to the north. With that accomplished, go west. That done, head west. And then, make an attempt to go north. That done, try to go east. That done, pick-up the cashew from the floor of the closet. And if you do that, you're the winner!
